{"type":"message","id":"5232492e","parentId":"e56a381b","timestamp":"2026-03-30T18:18:47.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Here’s how to add your Google Gemini and Anthropic API keys for OpenClaw:\n\n1. **Open your .env file** in your `.openclaw` folder (full path: `/Users/meshbot/.openclaw/.env`).\n\n2. **Add the following lines, replacing the placeholder text with your real API keys:**\n   ```\n   GEMINI_API_KEY=your-google-gemini-key-here\n   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-key-here\n   ```\n\n3. **Save the file.**\n\n4. **Restart OpenClaw** for the changes to take effect:\n   ```\n   openclaw gateway restart\n   ```\n\n**Tips:**\n- Make sure there are no extra spaces or quotes around your keys in the file.\n- If you don’t see a `.env` file, you can create it in your `.openclaw` directory.\n\nLet me know if you want me to check or edit the file for you!","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0134b14831f526be0069cabe7fc93c819486badc44b6c85c6b\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1","usage":{"input":10358,"output":211,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10569,"cost":{"input":0.020716,"output":0.0016879999999999998,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022403999999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774894713395,"responseId":"resp_0134b14831f526be0069cabe7a16088194a520c43cc56b8f2e"}}
